CustomField.formula: IF(Total_Deposits__c <= 500000000, "Up to $500 Million", IF(Total_Deposits__c >= 500000001 && Total_Deposits__c <= 1000000000, "$500 Million up to $1 Billion", IF(Total_Deposits__c >= 1000000001 && Total_Deposits__c <= 5000000000, "$1 Billion up to $5 Billion", IF(Total_Deposits__c >= 5000000001 && Total_Deposits__c <= 20000000000, "$5 Billion up to $20 Billion", IF(Total_Deposits__c >= 20000000001 && Total_Deposits__c <= 60000000000, "$20 Billion up to $60 Billion", IF(Total_Deposits__c >= 60000000001 && Total_Deposits__c <= 100000000000, "$60 Billion up to $100 Billion", IF(Total_Deposits__c >= 100000000001 && Total_Deposits__c <= 150000000000, "$100 Billion up to $150 Billion", IF(Total_Deposits__c >= 150000000001 && Total_Deposits__c <= 200000000000, "$150 Billion up to $200 Billion", IF(Total_Deposits__c >= 200000000001, "Over $200 Billion", null )))))))))
CustomField.label: AsM/PM Billing Tier
